                  Support
                </h1>
                <a
                  href="mailto: feedback@theathena.app"
                  class="text-slate-400 dark:text-slate-500 secondary-btn"
                >
                  Provide feedback
                </a>
                <a
                  href="mailto: features@theathena.app"
                  class="text-slate-400 dark:text-slate-500 secondary-btn"
                >
                  Request feature
                </a>
              </div>
      
              <div class="space-y-1">
                <h1 class="font-bold text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-300">
                  News
                </h1>
                <a
